---
description: "Always-on stack and environment defaults"
alwaysApply: true
---

Project stack defaults:
- Laravel 13
- Vue
- Tailwind CSS
- MySQL
- Laravel AI SDK
- OpenRouter

Environment defaults:
- Local development runs on Windows 11 with Cursor and Laravel Herd.
- When proposing or running terminal commands for local development, use PowerShell-compatible syntax.
- Production targets Laravel Forge on Linux VPS environments.

Cross-environment guidance:
- Prefer commands and paths that are explicit about OS differences when relevant.
- Call out Linux-vs-Windows differences early for deploy/runtime tasks (path separators, shell syntax, process management, permissions, case sensitivity).
